33:01.109 --> 33:03.982
-[FAST-PACED DRUM BEAT]

33:04.721 --> 33:07.289
-[BOAT MOTORS REVVING]

33:15.515 --> 33:16.995
-[MEN EXCLAIMING]

33:27.614 --> 33:29.572
-[ONLOOKERS EXCLAIMING]

33:32.923 --> 33:34.490
-YEAH! COME ON, LET'S GO!

33:34.621 --> 33:36.144
WOOHOO!

33:37.319 --> 33:39.495
-WHAT DO YOU SAY,
MATE? IT'S NOW OR NEVER.

33:39.626 --> 33:40.975
-GO FOR IT.

33:43.673 --> 33:45.501
-[FRENZIED GUITAR MUSIC]

33:47.242 --> 33:49.288
-LET'S GO, BARNETT!
GO, BARNETT, FASTER!

33:49.418 --> 33:50.419
-HERE WE GO!

33:50.550 --> 33:52.769
-[FRENZIED GUITAR MUSIC]

33:58.862 --> 34:01.691
-[LOGAN AND BARNETT SCREAM]

34:03.780 --> 34:05.695
-[ONLOOKERS EXCLAIMING]

34:05.826 --> 34:06.740
-[GASPS]

34:08.568 --> 34:10.699
-[FOREBODING MUSIC]

34:13.746 --> 34:15.705
-[ONLOOKERS EXCLAIMING]

34:17.272 --> 34:18.491
-[BOAT MOTOR REVVING]

34:18.621 --> 34:19.666
-TURN AROUND.

34:19.795 --> 34:21.320
-SOMEONE ELSE'LL PICK 'EM UP.

34:21.449 --> 34:22.929
-[INAUDIBLE] WE'RE TURNING
AROUND, DAMN IT, NOW!

34:23.452 --> 34:25.672
-[BOAT MOTOR REVS]

34:26.716 --> 34:28.675
-[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

34:31.156 --> 34:32.112
-[GASPS]

34:33.375 --> 34:35.551
-[BOAT MOTOR REVS]

34:40.339 --> 34:42.949
-[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

34:51.219 --> 34:52.306
-[GASPS]

34:53.917 --> 34:56.485
-[FRENZIED GUITAR MUSIC]

34:58.444 --> 35:00.446
-[BOAT MOTORS REVVING]

35:02.535 --> 35:03.797
-[GASPING]

35:05.929 --> 35:08.802
-[BREATHING HEAVILY]

35:10.108 --> 35:13.546
-BARNETT: I'M OKAY.
GET MATT. GET MATT.

35:20.074 --> 35:21.162
-[GRUNTS]

35:22.598 --> 35:24.252
[GROANS]

35:30.432 --> 35:31.607
-[BREATHING HEAVILY]

35:36.569 --> 35:38.397
[GRUNTS]

35:45.012 --> 35:46.144
-C.J, OVER THERE.

35:51.018 --> 35:52.324
BARNETT, YOU OKAY?

35:52.454 --> 35:53.238
-YEAH.

35:53.368 --> 35:54.282
-[BOAT MOTOR IDLES]

35:58.547 --> 35:59.766
-I NEED SOME HELP HERE.

36:01.898 --> 36:03.204
-[COUGHING]

36:03.335 --> 36:05.032
-[GRUNTS]

36:07.991 --> 36:09.471
-I'M ALL RIGHT. I'M ALL RIGHT.

36:09.602 --> 36:10.907
-OKAY. YOU ALMOST GOT KILLED.

36:11.865 --> 36:12.909
-[GRUNTS]

36:16.043 --> 36:17.262
-ARE YOU OKAY?
-LOGAN: YEAH.

36:23.964 --> 36:26.358
-[FRENZIED GUITAR MUSIC]

36:28.229 --> 36:30.275
-[ONLOOKERS CHEERING]

36:30.405 --> 36:31.972
-ANNOUNCER: AND
CROSSING THE FINISH LINE,

36:32.102 --> 36:34.192
THE WINNING TEAM, NEW ZEALAND!

36:35.976 --> 36:38.848
-[LIGHT MUSIC]

36:42.983 --> 36:45.768
-YEAH, THAT'LL BE
TOWER 12 FOR THAT GUY.

36:45.899 --> 36:46.943
-OKAY. THANK YOU.
-MITCH: THANK YOU, ROXY.

36:48.641 --> 36:50.599
MOM! [CHUCKLES]

36:50.730 --> 36:52.949
-I PREFER TO HANDLE
THIS MYSELF, ALL RIGHT?

36:53.080 --> 36:54.821
-I UNDERSTAND. I'LL
WAIT RIGHT HERE.

36:59.739 --> 37:01.567
-[PEOPLE TALKING INDISTINCTLY]

37:06.093 --> 37:08.574
-HEY, HI. WHAT
ARE YOU DOIN' HERE?

37:08.704 --> 37:10.097
-I CAME TO SAY GOODBYE.

37:10.228 --> 37:11.620
-GOODBYE?

37:11.751 --> 37:13.796
-WELL, CLIFF'S TAKING ME
ON A CRUISE TO ACAPULCO.

37:13.927 --> 37:19.062
-MOM. [CHUCKLES] YOU ARE NOT
GOING ON A CRUISE WITH HIM.

37:19.585 --> 37:22.849
-MITCH. I KNOW HOW YOU
FEEL ABOUT OUR RELATIONSHIP,

37:22.979 --> 37:26.418
BUT I'M NOT ASKING
FOR YOUR APPROVAL.

37:28.115 --> 37:30.291
LISTEN, DON'T MAKE ME
CRAWL BACK IN THE SHELL

37:30.422 --> 37:32.641
YOU FINALLY GOT ME
TO CRAWL OUT OF.

37:34.556 --> 37:36.254
I DIDN'T THINK I
WOULD FEEL THIS WAY.

37:39.039 --> 37:42.085
I FINALLY REALIZE THAT I
WILL NOT BE GROWING OLD

37:42.216 --> 37:43.217
WITH YOUR FATHER.

37:44.044 --> 37:46.655
AND I DON'T WANT TO
GROW OLD BY MYSELF.

37:52.139 --> 37:54.359
-IF YOU'RE HAPPY, I'M HAPPY.

37:55.011 --> 37:56.578
-OH, THANK YOU, DARLING.

37:57.710 --> 37:58.667
-WALK YOU TO YOUR CAR?

37:58.798 --> 38:00.582
-OH, YOU'RE SO GALANT.

38:05.761 --> 38:07.197
-NOW, YOU HAVE A GREAT TIME.

38:07.328 --> 38:08.721
-THANK YOU.

38:08.851 --> 38:10.331
-DON'T WORRY. I'LL
TAKE GOOD CARE OF HER.

38:11.506 --> 38:13.682
-SAY GOODBYE TO TRACY FOR ME.

38:13.813 --> 38:17.556
I'M SORRY IF I WAS A LITTLE
STANDOFFISH AT FIRST.

38:17.686 --> 38:22.517
I'M GLAD YOU FOUND HER. YOU TWO
WILL BE VERY HAPPY TOGETHER.

38:23.431 --> 38:25.825
-ALL RIGHT. BE GOOD, HUH.

38:25.955 --> 38:27.522
-I'LL TRY.

38:31.178 --> 38:32.353
-GOODBYE, SON.

38:32.484 --> 38:34.224
-I TOLD YOU TO
NEVER CALL ME THAT.

38:34.355 --> 38:35.661
-RIGHT.

38:37.140 --> 38:38.490
-[CAR ENGINE CRANKS]

38:44.713 --> 38:45.758
-BYE.

38:53.853 --> 38:54.723
-LOGAN!

38:57.509 --> 38:59.075
-BACK TO WORK SO SOON?

38:59.206 --> 39:01.077
-ALL I HAD WAS A SLIGHT
CONCUSSION, NO MAJOR DAMAGE.

39:01.730 --> 39:02.688
-THAT'S GOOD.

39:03.515 --> 39:06.126
-LOOK, UM, I WANTED TO SAY
THANKS FOR SAVING MY NECK

39:06.256 --> 39:07.127
THE OTHER DAY.

39:07.736 --> 39:09.303
-WELL, IT'S THE
LEAST I COULD'VE DONE.

39:09.434 --> 39:11.349
-NO, YOU COULD'VE GONE
ON AND WON THE RACE.

39:12.828 --> 39:14.526
-YEAH. WELL, I GUESS I'M
NOT AS TOUGH AS YOU THOUGHT.

39:15.614 --> 39:16.397
SEE YA LATER.

39:17.616 --> 39:20.880
-BY THE WAY, I HEAR
YOU GOT MARRIED.

39:21.750 --> 39:24.362
-YEAH. THAT'S RIGHT.

39:25.145 --> 39:26.189
-CONGRATULATIONS.

39:35.024 --> 39:37.766
-[PEOPLE TALKING INDISTINCTLY]

39:45.034 --> 39:46.253
-THIS IS FOR YOU.

39:54.740 --> 39:57.395
-[SORROWFUL MUSIC]

40:04.489 --> 40:06.012
-[CAR ENGINE CRANKS]

40:08.841 --> 40:12.366
-[SORROWFUL MUSIC]

40:22.855 --> 40:24.770
-[BIRDS SQUAWKING]

40:31.690 --> 40:32.473
-BOO!

40:32.604 --> 40:33.735
-[GASPS] GATOR!

40:33.866 --> 40:35.258
-[LAUGHING]

40:35.389 --> 40:36.869
OH, I WAS WONDERING WHEN
YOU WERE GONNA TURN UP.

40:37.652 --> 40:40.699
-OH, YOU LOOK, YOU
LOOK AS LOVELY AS EVER.

40:40.829 --> 40:42.048
-NO. WELL, HOW'S
IT GOIN' BACK HOME?

40:42.178 --> 40:43.963
-OH, THEY'RE MISSIN'
YOU DESPERATELY.

40:44.093 --> 40:45.486
THEY BEGGED ME TO BRING
YOU BACK, IN FACT.

40:45.617 --> 40:46.835
-[LAUGHS]

40:48.228 --> 40:49.925
IT'S GREAT TO SEE
YA LAUGHIN' AGAIN.

40:52.188 --> 40:54.190
LOGAN TELLS ME SOME YANK'S
HEAD OVER HEELS WITH YA.

40:56.236 --> 40:57.411
THOUGHT THAT WEREN'T
GONNA HAPPEN.

40:58.064 --> 40:59.761
-[SIGHS] I DIDN'T
WANT IT TO HAPPEN.

41:00.980 --> 41:02.155
-DID YOU TELL HIM?

41:02.895 --> 41:03.678
-NOT YET.

41:05.114 --> 41:06.464
-DON'T YOU THINK HE'S
GOT A RIGHT TO KNOW?

41:08.248 --> 41:09.989
-[SIGHS] I'M GONNA TELL HIM.

41:10.119 --> 41:10.946
-GATOR: WHEN?

41:11.991 --> 41:13.296
-AS SOON AS I GET UP THE NERVE.

41:13.819 --> 41:15.647
-THE LONGER YOU
LEAVE IT, TRACE,

41:17.257 --> 41:18.432
THE HARDER IT'S GONNA GET.

41:22.828 --> 41:23.655
-I KNOW.

41:27.702 --> 41:30.183
-[LIGHT MUSIC]

41:35.754 --> 41:38.234
-[END THEME PLAYING]
